resources.string: We are very much pleased to introduce ourselves as one of the business groups of Kerala with brand name “CONCEPT” having tagline “True and Transparent Relationship” catering the sectors of Automotive, Asset Management,Project Management, Agriculture and Training. The motive and belief of having long lasting personal and professional business have bought us the success in all the projects established from the day of inception; As we believe in the policy of “ Delighted Customers and Delighted Employee ”,we want to be in touch with our customers as much as we can so that we can serve them in the most efficient manner.For those who treat time as life we have great career at Concept and fantastic positions open for driven and learning oriented individuals.
